1 Alert version 
The pigpio library(https://abyz.me.uk/rpi/pigpio/) is used in Send_Alert65BPap.c 
and Receive_Alert65BPap.c . You can easily to install pigpio library 
using apt in raspberry pi. 

2 Poling version
You need to install BCM2835, if you want to use SendBCM2835Pap.c 
and ReceiveBCM2835Pap.c .

a. Download bcm2835/bcm2835-1.75.tar.gz  or newer from
   https://www.airspayce.com/mikem/bcm2835/index.html

b. Install automake
   sudo apt install automake

c. Compile the bcm2835-1.75 
   tar zxvf bcm2835-1.75.tar.gz
   cd bcm2835-1.75 
   ./configure
   make
   sudo make install

3. Compile Programs
Send_Alert65BPap.c Receive_Alert65BPap.c SendBCM2835Pap.c and ReceiveBCM2835Pap.c
are easily compiled using "make". 

